tanceof，Object.prototype.toString","slug":"检测变量类型之typeof，instanceof，Object-prototype-toString","date":"2021-03-07T09:12:32.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:20:50.979Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/检测变量类型之typeof，instanceof，Object-prototype-toString.json","excerpt":"<p>在JS中有时候是需要对一个变量进行检测的，检测到这个变量是什么类型之后，我们就可以做相应的处理。<br></p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"在JS中有时候是需要对一个变量进行检测的，检测到这个变量是什么类型之后，我们就可以做相应的处理。<br><br>方法一typeoftypeof方法主要用于基本类型的检测，在检测Boolean，number，undefined，string的时候非常好用。比如：1<br>2<br>","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]},{"title":"纯JS实现像素逐渐显示","slug":"纯JS实现像素逐渐显示","date":"2021-03-07T08:51:41.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:20:34.846Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/纯JS实现像素逐渐显示.json","excerpt":"<p>就是对于新手的我，以前从来没有做过对像素进行操作的实例。于是把资料书找了出来，实现了这个功能，比较简单，大神勿喷。下面是效果图，因为重在思路，效果就简陋一些。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":"//yoursite.com/2021/03/07/纯JS实现像素逐渐显示/1.png","content":null,"text":"就是对于新手的我，以前从来没有做过对像素进行操作的实例。于是把资料书找了出来，实现了这个功能，比较简单，大神勿喷。下面是效果图，因为重在思路，效果就简陋一些。 [Figure] 其中31到35行的for循环还是一样将原矩形的像素点传递给新矩形。但是这一次是用iNum来实现分批次的","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]},{"title":"跨浏览器之创建和处理XML","slug":"跨浏览器之创建和处理XML","date":"2021-03-07T09:03:24.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:21:08.174Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/跨浏览器之创建和处理XML.json","excerpt":"<p>XML在不同浏览器下的创建方式，解析成DOM方式和序列化方式都有很大的差异。<br></p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"XML在不同浏览器下的创建方式，解析成DOM方式和序列化方式都有很大的差异。<br><br>主要区分的是1.IE9.0之前版本中的XML2.DOM2级核心下的XML为了解决这种差异，编写了一个函数用以在任何浏览器下都能解析和序列化。首先建立一个函数，用以在IE9之前创建xml空文","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]},{"title":"跨浏览器之事件处理程序","slug":"跨浏览器之事件处理程序","date":"2021-03-07T09:17:18.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:21:51.605Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/跨浏览器之事件处理程序.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>上次说到了JS中事件处理程序在DOM0级和DOM2级和IE中是不同的，每个都有自己的添加和移除事件处理程序的形式。</p>\n<p>那要将这些差异进行统一化。避免这种差异。对于顺序问题，我们应该要先将最经常使用的放在最上面把兼容性最好的放在最下面，也就是实现向后兼容。<br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">addEvent</span>(<span class=\"params\">obj,type,handle</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">2</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(obj.addEventListener)&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//兼容DOM3级</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">3</span>         obj.addEventListener(type,handle,<span class=\"literal\">false</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">4</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">5</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(obj.attachEvent)&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//兼容DOM0级</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">6</span>         obj.attachEvent(<span class=\"string\">\"on\"</span>+type,handle);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">7</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">8</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//IE</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"number\">9</span>         <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> type = <span class=\"string\">\"on\"</span>+type;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">10</span>         obj.type = handle;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">11</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">12</span> &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">13</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">14</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">removeEvent</span>(<span class=\"params\">obj,type,handle</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">15</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(obj.removeEventListener)&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//兼容DOM3级</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">16</span>         obj.removeEventListener(type,handle,<span class=\"literal\">false</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">17</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">18</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(obj.detachEvent)&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//兼容DOM0级</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">19</span>         obj.detachEvent(<span class=\"string\">\"on\"</span>+type,handle);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">20</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">21</span>     <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//IE</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">22</span>         <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> type = <span class=\"string\">\"on\"</span>+type;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">23</span>         obj.type = <span class=\"literal\">null</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">24</span>     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">25</span> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>这端代码能实现在各种浏览器下处理好事件处理程序。</p>\n","text":"上次说到了JS中事件处理程序在DOM0级和DOM2级和IE中是不同的，每个都有自己的添加和移除事件处理程序的形式。那要将这些差异进行统一化。避免这种差异。对于顺序问题，我们应该要先将最经常使用的放在最上面把兼容性最好的放在最下面，也就是实现向后兼容。<br>1<br>2<br>3","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]},{"title":"跨浏览器之封装ajax","slug":"跨浏览器之封装ajax","date":"2021-03-07T09:00:51.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:21:41.243Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/跨浏览器之封装ajax.json","excerpt":"<p>ajax是异步的javascript和XML，主要用于前端后端的数据传送。<br></p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"ajax是异步的javascript和XML，主要用于前端后端的数据传送。<br><br>要封装一个ajax，使之能相应的平稳退化，第一步就是创建一个XHR（XMLHttpRequest）对象。以下代码是在各种浏览器下创建xhr对象：1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<b","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":18,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]}]}